And they don't dilute the whiskey,

427
00:20:13,710 --> 00:20:18,030
正如一个紧凑的计划容不得半点干扰
the way a tight plan doesn't obscure its objectives.

428
00:20:20,050 --> 00:20:22,120
这是防止我对你出手吗
Is that to protect you from me?

429
00:20:22,120 --> 00:20:25,240
不  只是有助于对付门口你那位哨兵
No, but it might help against your sentry at the door.

430
00:20:25,480 --> 00:20:27,780
填字游戏下的消音枪
The silencer poking out of his crossword section

431
00:20:27,780 --> 00:20:29,390
