439
00:20:57,120 --> 00:20:59,190
你反应迅速
You're good on your feet,

440
00:20:59,210 --> 00:21:01,350
思路清楚  判断准确
and you know your way around an asset.

441
00:21:01,720 --> 00:21:03,800
前中情局的
Ex-CIA?

442
00:21:06,490 --> 00:21:08,130
高手
Smashing.

443
00:21:08,610 --> 00:21:11,450
