- How much do you cost? - Not for sale.

444
00:21:11,450 --> 00:21:12,910
你为威尔德工作
You're working for Veldt?

445
00:21:12,910 --> 00:21:15,870
额外保镖之类的
Some kind of additional security?

446
00:21:16,430 --> 00:21:17,670
这不重要
It doesn't matter.

447
00:21:18,710 --> 00:21:22,230
重要的是  你被发现了
What matters is-- if you were caught,

448
00:21:22,230 --> 00:21:23,910
我干嘛不杀那妻子呢
why didn't I kill the wife?

449
00:21:24,130 --> 00:21:27,580
因为医生还没有违背你的规则
Because the doctor hasn't broken any of your rules yet.

450
00:21:27,580 --> 00:21:31,410
确实  但我的风度是有底限的
Exactly, but my sense of propriety has its limits.

451
00:21:31,550 --> 00:21:34,500
离公园远点  离那妻子远点
Now stay out of the park and away from the wife.

452
00:21:34,740 --> 00:21:37,640
这不是你的游戏  没人邀请你来玩
This isn't your game, and no one's invited you to play.

453
