别试探我的底线
Don't test me.

454
00:21:40,080 --> 00:21:41,970
我预想了所有的可能
I was expecting everything.

455
00:21:42,010 --> 00:21:43,540
你没预想到我
You weren't expecting me.

456
00:22:17,030 --> 00:22:18,730
我们很快就准备好了  医生
We'll be ready for you soon, doctor.

457
00:22:26,960 --> 00:22:29,680
