Dr. Enright, I hate to bother you.

459
00:22:38,070 --> 00:22:39,230
你来这儿干吗
What are you doing in here?

460
00:22:39,940 --> 00:22:42,860
还记得我吗  今天早前见过
Do you remember me? From earlier today?

461
00:22:43,950 --> 00:22:45,610
你是那名捐赠者  克灵
You're that donor--Crane.

462
00:22:46,080 --> 00:22:49,490
