but you have to trust us.

466
00:22:57,860 --> 00:22:58,950
你是谁
Who are you?

467
00:22:59,130 --> 00:23:00,870
我怎么知道你不是那人的手下
How do I know you're not working for that man?

468
00:23:00,970 --> 00:23:03,890
这场手术本该在二十分钟前开始
This procedure was supposed to start 20 minutes ago,

469
00:23:03,990 --> 00:23:05,950
但是我更改了医院血库库存
but I altered the hospital blood records

470
00:23:05,950 --> 00:23:07,600
以推迟手术
to delay the surgery.

471
00:23:08,150 --> 00:23:10,710
马上就会有护士来解释这件事
In a moment, a nurse will come in here to explain the error.

472
00:23:10,810 --> 00:23:12,310
现在仔细听我说
Now listen to me carefully.

473
00:23:12,720 --> 00:23:14,620
我们不能让韦斯利起疑心
We can't make Wesley suspicious,

474
00:23:14,650 --> 00:23:17,420
