but we'll save Amy before you have to make the incision.

475
00:23:20,010 --> 00:23:22,160
医生  我去楼下检查过O型阴性血的库存记录了
Doctor, I checked the O-Neg records downstairs.

476
00:23:22,160 --> 00:23:24,540
是电脑系统出错  他们正在修复
It's a computer mix-up. They're fixing the glitch.

477
00:23:24,540 --> 00:23:25,840
