We have plenty of blood reserves.

478
00:23:25,850 --> 00:23:27,630
一会儿就可以开始了
We should be ready to go shortly.

479
00:23:28,960 --> 00:23:32,050
莉兹  这位是克灵医生
Liz, this is Dr. Crane.

480
00:23:33,280 --> 00:23:36,480
