I brought him in as a second scrub if I need help.

481
00:23:36,730 --> 00:23:38,310
听您安排  医生
Whatever you say, doctor.

482
00:23:41,750 --> 00:23:42,940
救救我
Help me.

483
00:23:43,360 --> 00:23:45,880
救救我和艾米
Help us, Amy and I.

484
00:23:46,510 --> 00:23:48,000
否则我不知道自己会怎样
Or I don't know what I'll do.

485
00:23:57,880 --> 00:24:00,420
麦蒂已经进入手术室了  里瑟先生
Maddy has officially gone into the operating room, Mr. Reese.

486
00:24:00,420 --> 00:24:01,580
公园那边进展如何
How are things in the park?

487
00:24:01,610 --> 00:24:03,830
我跟韦斯利那一杯喝得不怎么样
My drink with Wesley didn't go so well,

488
00:24:03,900 --> 00:24:06,050
