but we can count another one of his operatives out.

489
00:24:07,520 --> 00:24:09,250
他装了自己的摄像头
He brought his own cameras

490
00:24:09,860 --> 00:24:12,310
监控了公园的每个角落
and has every inch of this park monitored.

491
00:24:12,540 --> 00:24:15,210
