but after that injection of heparin, Veldt's a time bomb.

506
00:25:21,050 --> 00:25:22,570
稍微切错一点点
any wrong incision at this point--

507
00:25:23,240 --> 00:25:23,900
等等
Hold on.

508
00:25:26,140 --> 00:25:27,680
陶先生  你有何发现
Mr. Tao, what did you find?

509
00:25:27,680 --> 00:25:29,190
芬奇  老兄
Finch! Boobie--

510
00:25:29,570 --> 00:25:31,790
