and found a proposed multimillion-dollar project

513
00:25:35,910 --> 00:25:37,530
是关于海上风电的
for offshore wind farms.

514
00:25:37,620 --> 00:25:39,680
威尔德驳回了
Veldt dismissed it.

515
00:25:39,840 --> 00:25:42,630
