One wrong step, and it's over.

649
00:31:31,430 --> 00:31:32,340
讲  芬奇
Yes, Finch.

650
00:31:32,340 --> 00:31:34,340
里瑟先生  根据麦蒂的时间表
Mr. Reese, according to Maddy's timetable,

